# OAuth client credentials for built-in uploaders. The committed Secrets.cs holds empty
# placeholder values (so CI / fresh clones build); maintainers create Secrets.Local.cs in the
# same folder with the real Client IDs / Secrets, and the .csproj swaps them in via a
# conditional Compile Remove on Secrets.cs when the Local file exists.
src/ShareQ.Uploaders/Secrets.Local.cs

